# Dashboard Guide

Run dashboard:
cd dashboard
npm run dev

Routes:
- /auth: test auth API
- /explain: view explainability output + chart
- /fairness: fairness dashboard charts
- /ghost: ghost scan + demo seed + table

## Recommended Demo Flow
1) /auth: run face low confidence → ESCALATE
2) /explain: explain same VID → shows rule weights
3) /fairness: run multiple methods → shows disparity chart
4) /ghost: seed old VID → scan → flagged candidate appears

Planned:
- /enrolment (official dataset analytics)
- /demographic (official dataset analytics)
- /biometric (official dataset analytics)
